verbose_text: Consistent with adequate iron and vitamin B-12 status, Pinto et al. found similar levels of ferritin, transferrin, hemoglobin, and vitamin B-12 that were within normal limits in 11 subjects with PKU consuming AA-MF in combination with Glytactin GMP-MF for ~ 13 months [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: levels of ferritin, transferrin, hemoglobin, and vitamin B-12
